snippet: MUSCHE--Dorothy E.,age 75, passed away on May 14th at Mary Manning Walsh hospice in New York City following a long battle with leukemia. Preceded in death by her parents, Ruth and Chester Musche, and sister, Geraldine, she will be buried next to her parents in Portland, Maine. 1/3
